
| Endpoint | URL |
|---|---|
| Home | `http://localhost:8080/` |
| All items | `http://localhost:8080/item` |
| Single item | `http://localhost:8080/item/1` |
| All orders | `http://localhost:8080/order` |
| Single order | `http://localhost:8080/order/1` |


Here are all the URLs:

---

### Items
| Method | URL | Body |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `http://localhost:8080/item` | — |
| GET | `http://localhost:8080/item/1` | — |
| POST | `http://localhost:8080/item` | `{"name": "Pen", "quantity": 5}` |
| PUT | `http://localhost:8080/item/1` | `{"name": "Pen Updated", "quantity": 10}` |
| DELETE | `http://localhost:8080/item/1` | — |

